settings.testimonial_content: My BFF Jacky has had stomach troubles for years. Thanks to gutsy’s hypo-allergenic trekker fuel, those issues are in the past!
It’s funny how we always consider our own footprint when thinking about sustainability. Gutsy reduces our pet’s paw print too!
My border collie is a real hiker, he’s more wolf than dog! A nutritious meal that’s rich in proteins is exactly what she needed.
